Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.67,0:02:07.07,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}哇喔ー！ 歡迎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.07,0:02:08.47,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}哇喔ー！ 哈囉
