Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.24,0:02:16.59,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2\an1}是怎樣 別再碰我 不要靠近我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.31,0:02:16.68,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2\an3}您好可愛！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.91,0:02:19.48,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}居然滿口是愛 無法接受
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.48,0:02:22.26,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2\an1}我不需要妳的喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.80,0:02:22.53,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2\an3}我想和您親近！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.53,0:02:27.90,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2\an1}應該要 更加若無其事才好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.62,0:02:28.95,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2\an3}我會保護大小姐的！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.15,0:02:30.74,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2\an1}不是愛 是侵略吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.74,0:02:33.72,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}喜歡太過強烈了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.72,0:02:34.96,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}好煩 好煩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.96,0:02:35.67,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}好煩？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.67,0:02:36.37,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}好煩！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.37,0:02:39.36,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}只能討厭了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.36,0:02:40.61,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}好煩 好煩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.61,0:02:41.45,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}好煩？！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.45,0:02:42.06,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}好煩！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.06,0:02:47.89,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}大人啊 像個大人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.41,0:02:56.14,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}如果真的是想和我更加親近
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.14,0:03:01.75,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}就應該更加理解我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.75,0:03:04.75,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}盡興 盡興 盡興 盡興
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.75,0:03:07.38,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}玩樂之後或許某一天
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.69,0:03:11.67,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}我會改變心意吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.67,0:03:16.25,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2\an1}不 是我的錯覺
