Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.05,0:03:20.39,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}哇喔ー！ 歡迎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.39,0:03:21.87,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}哇喔ー！ 哈囉
